            <h1 itemprop="headline">As predicted, more branch prediction processor attacks are discovered</h1>
            <h2 itemprop="description">New attack focuses on a different part of the branch prediction system.</h2>
            <section class="post-meta">

  
<p class="byline" itemprop="author creator" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
